Company Overview of Capital Fund Management S.A.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capital Fund Management S.A. is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. The firm launches and manages hedge funds. It invests in the public equity, fixed income markets, and alternative investment across the globe. The firm also invests in derivatives, and options. It employs quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. Capital Fund Management S.A. was founded in 1991 and is based in Paris, France.


