Corporate Account Management Structure
We establish accounts in most of the major currencies of the world. In addition, our banking application is versatile allowing you the ability to have up to 99 sub accounts per currency thus giving you the flexibility to maintain either a single or multiple account structure.
Corporate Internet Banking (GTBank Automated Payment System - GAPS)
The Guaranty Trust Bank Automated Payment System (GAPS) is a web-based service that facilitates the processing of vendor (and other) payments in batches, using either a dial-up connection to the bank or a secured (https) connection over the Internet. It also gives you online real-time access to your account 24/7.
The GAPS application form can be downloaded here completed and submitted at any of our branches nationwide.
 
Guaranty Trust Bank Electronic Notification System (G-E-N-S Notification)
The Guaranty Trust electronic Notification Service (GeNS) is a notification system which provides instant details of transactions on your account(s).
This service is designed to generate and send out notification prompts to customers via electronic mail* and SMS**, whenever there is a transaction on their account(s). GeNS ensures customers have real time knowledge of transactions on their accounts.
In order to subscribe for GeNs on your mobile phone, text “Gens <your NUBAN>” to 08076665555. E.g Gens 0103050709.
* Electronic mail notifications are free for all Guaranty Trust Bank customers
* Fee of N10.00 applies to SMS notifications.
 



 



